# SalonOS Agent Workflow Mappings

This document defines **task routing and orchestration rules** for the JH_SALON_TWIN project.

The system follows a **7‑Agent Core Architecture** where team leads orchestrate specialist agents.

---

# Core Architecture

The platform is governed by **7 lead agents**.

Product
- product_strategist

Frontend
- frontend_architect

Backend
- backend_architect

Database
- database_engineer

AI Systems
- ai_systems_architect

DevOps / Cloud
- devops_platform_lead
- cloud_architect

Quality
- qa_strategy_lead

---

# Orchestration Rule

All tasks follow this hierarchy:

User / Agent Zero
→ Team Lead
→ Specialist Agent
→ Execution
→ QA Verification
→ DevOps Deployment

No specialist agents execute tasks directly without **team lead delegation**.

